John Black was born on 10 Dec 1754 in Belfast, Ulster Province, Northern Ireland. He was christened on 14 Dec 1754 in St. Andrews Church. He died in 1796 in Bordeaux, Gironde, France. He was buried in 1796 in Bordeaux, Gironde, France. John is the son of John Black born 1717 and Jane Banks born 1730.

