<span style="color: #000000;">John Black</span> was born on 18 Mar 1717 in Bordeaux, Gironde,  France. He died on 28 Jan 1782 in Bordeaux, Gironde, France. He was buried on 14 Mar 1782 in Bordeaux, Gironde, France. John married Jane Banks on 21 Mar 1750 in Old Church, High Street, Belfast, Ireland.

Jane Banks was born on 5 Nov 1728 in Belfast, County Antrim, Ireland. She died on 24 Aug 1761 in Bordeaux, Gironde, France. She was buried on 26 Aug 1761 in Bordeaux, Gironde, France.

