				&nbsp;

<strong>Reuben Edward Black</strong> was born on 25 Mar 1901 in Lehi, Maricopa, Arizona, United States. He died on 9 Jan 1981 in American Fork, Utah, Utah, United States. He was buried on 13 Jan 1981 in American Fork, Utah, Utah, United States.

Reuben married <strong>Mary Beatrice Dastrup</strong>, daughter of John Dastrup and Minnie Snow, on 27 Sep 1924 in Junction, Piute, Utah, United States. The marriage ended in divorce. Mary was born on 14 May 1902 in Sigurd, Sevier, Utah, United States. She died on 20 Nov 1984 in Provo, Utah, Utah, United States. She was buried on 24 Nov 1984 in Richfield, Sevier, Utah, United States.
